317
00:27:36,400 --> 00:27:37,200
but each one

318
00:27:38,279 --> 00:27:39,160
is a sign of their

319
00:27:39,160 --> 00:27:40,480
wholehearted care for me.

320
00:27:42,200 --> 00:27:43,559
They treat me like family.

321
00:27:45,440 --> 00:27:46,880
And I treat them like family too.

322
00:27:49,359 --> 00:27:50,960
So before I leave,

323
00:27:52,920 --> 00:27:54,640
I want to do something for them.

324
00:28:05,279 --> 00:28:06,279
Dad, try some.

325
00:28:07,599 --> 00:28:09,440
The seafood noodles here are great.

326
00:28:11,480 --> 00:28:12,000
Okay.

327
00:28:30,039 --> 00:28:30,839
Here's a hundred thousand.

328
00:28:31,519 --> 00:28:32,920
Consider this payment

329
00:28:32,920 --> 00:28:33,839
