339
00:28:50,559 --> 00:28:51,799
Better to have money than not.

340
00:28:56,400 --> 00:28:56,920
Yes.

341
00:28:57,359 --> 00:28:58,119
You're right.

342
00:28:58,559 --> 00:28:59,839
No one turns down money.

343
00:29:00,720 --> 00:29:01,240
Alright.

344
00:29:02,359 --> 00:29:03,119
I'll take it.

345
00:29:03,720 --> 00:29:05,240
