346
00:29:25,119 --> 00:29:27,359
Oone, ten, a hundred, a thousand...

347
00:29:35,559 --> 00:29:35,960
Here.

348
00:29:36,640 --> 00:29:37,119
Take a look.

349
00:29:41,640 --> 00:29:43,279
