351
00:29:44,880 --> 00:29:45,759
But I have to.

352
00:29:47,720 --> 00:29:48,440
I admit,

353
00:29:48,759 --> 00:29:50,319
back then, I looked after Ye

354
00:29:50,359 --> 00:29:51,319
