355
00:29:52,119 --> 00:29:53,640
But after all this time together,

356
00:29:53,640 --> 00:29:54,640
I've come to think of her

357
00:29:54,640 --> 00:29:55,720
as my own niece.

358
00:29:56,519 --> 00:29:57,200
So thank you

359
00:29:57,200 --> 00:29:58,240
for lending me this money.

360
00:29:59,359 --> 00:30:01,319
Even if it's for Ye's sake,

361
00:30:01,720 --> 00:30:03,480
