366
00:30:19,160 --> 00:30:19,640
Here.
Auntie.

367
00:30:23,200 --> 00:30:23,759
Alright.

368
00:30:24,480 --> 00:30:25,759
No need to see me off.

369
00:30:25,960 --> 00:30:27,359
