370
00:30:27,599 --> 00:30:28,599
Even better.

371
00:30:28,640 --> 00:30:29,680
Just stay in Zhazhating.

372
00:30:29,839 --> 00:30:30,920
I'll cover your room and board.

373
00:30:31,480 --> 00:30:32,119
