376
00:30:38,400 --> 00:30:39,160
Ye,

377
00:30:40,400 --> 00:30:41,400
Grandma and I

378
00:30:42,160 --> 00:30:44,599
wanted to give you something

379
00:30:44,640 --> 00:30:45,839
