380
00:30:46,880 --> 00:30:47,559
But Xuan...

381
00:30:48,680 --> 00:30:49,680
Xuan Island is gone.

382
00:30:51,000 --> 00:30:51,960
So we don't have

383
00:30:51,960 --> 00:30:53,599
