389
00:31:07,079 --> 00:31:07,759
Grandma.

390
00:31:09,200 --> 00:31:10,839
Grandma, you're not old.

391
00:31:11,519 --> 00:31:13,279
You'll live to a hundred.

392
00:31:14,839 --> 00:31:17,160
I can't possibly live that long.

393
00:31:17,880 --> 00:31:19,079
I say you will, so you will.

394
00:31:20,559 --> 00:31:22,160
Finish knitting my scarf.

395
00:31:23,359 --> 00:31:24,839
I'll come back for it next time.

396
00:31:25,559 --> 00:31:26,039
Okay.

397
00:31:26,839 --> 00:31:28,400
I'll be here waiting for you.

398
00:31:29,160 --> 00:31:30,319
Come back whenever you have time.

399
00:31:32,200 --> 00:31:32,880
Grandma,

400
00:31:36,240 --> 00:31:38,279
I'm going to miss you all so much.

401
00:31:39,480 --> 00:31:40,720
I'll get you

402
00:31:40,720 --> 00:31:41,880
