408
00:32:01,319 --> 00:32:02,000
Ye.

409
00:32:02,960 --> 00:32:03,599
Time to go.

410
00:32:11,720 --> 00:32:12,240
Go on.

411
00:32:13,039 --> 00:32:14,640
Don't keep your dad waiting.

412
00:32:17,000 --> 00:32:18,079
Don't cry.

413
00:32:18,559 --> 00:32:20,440
Leave with the same smile you came with.

414
00:32:21,000 --> 00:32:22,000
Don't let people think

415
00:32:22,279 --> 00:32:24,240
