416
00:32:32,799 --> 00:32:33,319
Okay.

417
00:32:34,039 --> 00:32:34,720
Grandma.

418
00:32:35,160 --> 00:32:36,039
I'm going now.
Okay.

419
00:32:37,759 --> 00:32:38,400
Alright.

420
00:32:39,519 --> 00:32:40,839
Good girl.

421
00:32:46,480 --> 00:32:47,440
Auntie Yufen.

422
00:32:48,640 --> 00:32:49,519
Auntie Shanxi.

423
00:32:50,880 --> 00:32:51,559
Auntie.

424
00:32:53,720 --> 00:32:54,440
I'm leaving.

425
00:32:58,359 --> 00:32:59,000
Kyle.

426
00:33:00,160 --> 00:33:00,880
Big G.

427
00:33:04,640 --> 00:33:05,359
