434
00:33:20,079 --> 00:33:20,599
Right.

435
00:33:21,599 --> 00:33:23,000
I already talked to Ye Yingjian.

436
00:33:23,880 --> 00:33:25,519
He'll keep you all studying.

437
00:33:26,000 --> 00:33:26,759
I'll send you

438
00:33:26,759 --> 00:33:28,160
