491
00:38:38,039 --> 00:38:39,320
But that's in the past.

492
00:38:40,280 --> 00:38:41,440
Let's just give each other an out.

493
00:38:42,440 --> 00:38:43,280
We'll still have to
deal with them.

494
00:38:50,440 --> 00:38:51,760
