498
00:39:12,000 --> 00:39:12,599
Mr. Qing.

499
00:39:13,039 --> 00:39:13,719
Ye.

500
00:39:14,079 --> 00:39:14,519
Hello, Mrs. Meng.

501
00:39:14,519 --> 00:39:15,599
Let me take a look.

502
00:39:15,760 --> 00:39:16,440
Hello, Mr. Meng.
Good.

503
00:39:18,360 --> 00:39:18,880
Great.

504
00:39:19,360 --> 00:39:20,239
I can finally

505
00:39:20,280 --> 00:39:21,440
