506
00:39:21,639 --> 00:39:22,079
Have a seat.
Mr. Qing, sit.

507
00:39:23,320 --> 00:39:24,000
Qing, sit.

508
00:39:24,320 --> 00:39:25,119
- Glad you're back.
- Sit.

509
00:39:28,320 --> 00:39:29,039
Alright.

510
00:39:29,280 --> 00:39:30,320
Let's

511
00:39:30,960 --> 00:39:32,440
