- Bring out the food.

514
00:39:35,920 --> 00:39:36,320
Okay.
Yes, yes.

515
00:39:37,239 --> 00:39:38,239
- Bring out the food.
- Bring out the food.

516
00:39:38,760 --> 00:39:39,960
I'm just a little excited

517
00:39:40,079 --> 00:39:41,079
to see you both.

518
00:39:43,039 --> 00:39:43,719
Qing,

519
00:39:44,280 --> 00:39:45,480
life has its ups and downs.

520
00:39:46,039 --> 00:39:47,280
Thankfully, it was just a false alarm.

521
00:39:47,679 --> 00:39:48,440
That wasn't easy.

522
00:39:49,079 --> 00:39:50,480
This toast is for you.

523
00:39:51,039 --> 00:39:52,480
To your return to the top of your career.

524
00:39:53,039 --> 00:39:54,000
Bottoms up.

525
00:39:54,920 --> 00:39:55,719
We'll join you.

526
00:39:58,760 --> 00:39:59,679
Lately, Ye and I

527
00:40:00,280 --> 00:40:01,639
have really relied on

528
00:40:02,519 --> 00:40:04,079
all of you for your support.

529
00:40:05,440 --> 00:40:06,159
Going forward,

530
00:40:06,679 --> 00:40:07,840
I'll need your

531
00:40:08,239 --> 00:40:09,039
continued support.

532
00:40:09,800 --> 00:40:11,079
Let's keep working together.

533
00:40:12,199 --> 00:40:12,639
Here.

534
00:40:13,320 --> 00:40:14,440
I'd like to toast you all.

535
00:40:14,639 --> 00:40:15,440
Mr. Qing, you're too kind.
Here.

536
00:40:16,840 --> 00:40:17,360
Mr. Qing.

537
00:40:23,679 --> 00:40:24,199
Ye,

538
00:40:25,039 --> 00:40:26,679
why don't you toast Mr. and Mrs. Meng?

539
00:40:29,119 --> 00:40:29,760
Okay.

540
00:40:33,960 --> 00:40:34,559
Mr...

541
00:40:35,800 --> 00:40:37,079
Mr. and Mrs. Meng, let me toast you.

542
00:40:38,920 --> 00:40:39,679
Alright, alright.

543
00:40:40,719 --> 00:40:41,280
Ye.

544
00:40:41,480 --> 00:40:42,480
Have a seat.

545
00:40:44,599 --> 00:40:45,519
Ye, you look

546
00:40:45,960 --> 00:40:47,760
