550
00:40:52,920 --> 00:40:54,000
It made me

551
00:40:54,079 --> 00:40:55,880
so worried and sad.

552
00:40:57,119 --> 00:40:58,519
But I'm glad you're back now.

553
00:40:58,800 --> 00:40:59,719
Just look forward.

554
00:41:00,960 --> 00:41:01,639
Look forward.

555
00:41:02,719 --> 00:41:03,800
Thanks, Mrs. Meng.

556
00:41:04,760 --> 00:41:05,840
Actually, I was doing pretty well

557
00:41:05,840 --> 00:41:06,760
