566
00:41:22,440 --> 00:41:22,920
Qing Ye,

567
00:41:23,320 --> 00:41:24,000
I believe in you.

568
00:41:26,960 --> 00:41:27,880
I won.

569
00:41:30,760 --> 00:41:31,760
Life's full of

570
00:41:31,840 --> 00:41:34,079
different flavors. Face it with a smile.

571
00:41:34,199 --> 00:41:35,519
Play it right,

572
00:41:35,840 --> 00:41:37,119
and you're the winner.

573
00:41:37,960 --> 00:41:40,440
Every extra day is a gain.

574
00:41:41,119 --> 00:41:42,440
Just being alive is a victory.

575
00:41:43,119 --> 00:41:43,760
Qing Ye.

576
00:41:45,480 --> 00:41:46,880
You're a born explorer.

577
00:41:48,440 --> 00:41:49,440
Time to set sail.

578
00:41:50,679 --> 00:41:52,199
Go conquer your vast ocean.

579
00:41:52,679 --> 00:41:53,320
It's precisely because of

580
00:41:53,320 --> 00:41:54,719
