589
00:42:21,360 --> 00:42:22,480
Thanks for treating us, Meng.

590
00:42:22,519 --> 00:42:23,599
Come over to my place anytime.

591
00:42:23,719 --> 00:42:24,880
I'll make your favorite dishes.

592
00:42:25,280 --> 00:42:26,320
Next one's on me.

593
00:42:26,599 --> 00:42:27,039
Okay.

594
00:42:28,440 --> 00:42:29,360
Let's get together often.

595
00:42:30,480 --> 00:42:31,440
Let's go, honey.

596
00:42:32,119 --> 00:42:33,320
Mr. Qing, we're going now.

597
00:42:33,679 --> 00:42:34,119
Okay.
Let's go.
Bye.

598
00:42:34,960 --> 00:42:35,840
Mr. and Mrs. Meng, bye.

599
00:42:36,360 --> 00:42:37,320
Come visit often.

600
00:42:44,159 --> 00:42:44,639
Dad.

601
00:42:45,639 --> 00:42:46,960
You go back first.

602
00:42:47,760 --> 00:42:49,159
I want to walk around by myself.

603
00:42:51,760 --> 00:42:52,159
Okay.

604
00:42:53,119 --> 00:42:54,559
I'll have Sun come get you later.
